[Slurp] Halo…

52:14.881 --> 52:18.009
teman lama.

52:21.805 --> 52:22.806
[kegentingan]

52:36.278 --> 52:37.279
Pergi.

52:38.697 --> 52:39.739
Sekarang.

52:55.797 --> 52:57.215
[mengaum]

53:01.928 --> 53:03.930
